4a14\" class=\"Task\"><h2 aria-controls=\"aria-mchla35b4a14\" class=\"Name\">Take a photo or record a video</h2><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-mchla35b4a14\"><ul><li><p><em>Take a photo or video of yourself:</em> See <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/photo-booth/pbhlp3714a9d/mac\" class=\"URL\">Take a photo or record a video in Photo Booth</a>.</p></li><li><p><em>Take a photo or video of your screen:</em> See <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=take-a-screenshot&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MH26782&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Take screenshots or screen recordings</a>.</p></li></ul></div></div><div id=\"mchld0c0924b\" class=\"Task\"><h2 aria-controls=\"aria-mchld0c0924b\" class=\"Name\">Improve image quality</h2><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-mchld0c0924b\"><ul><li><p><em>Clean the camera:</em> Use a soft, lint-free cloth to wipe the camera.</p></li><li><p><em>Adjust lighting:</em> Make sure you are well lit from the front, without a lot of light behind you; for example, with windows in front of you.</p></li><li><p><em>Improve your Wi-Fi connection:</em> Move closer to your Wi-Fi router and make sure there are no objects impeding its signal, such as walls.</p></li><li><p><em>Change app settings:</em> Certain apps may allow you to adjust camera quality. Check your app settings and adjust if needed.</p></li><li><p><em>Use your iPhone as a webcam:</em> Connect to a supported iPhone and use its camera instead of the built-in Mac camera. See <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=use-iphone-as-a-webcam&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL77879B8A&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Use your iPhone as a webcam on Mac</a>.</p></li></ul></div></div><div id=\"mchlad460728\" class=\"Task\"><h2 aria-controls=\"aria-mchlad460728\" class=\"Name\">Troubleshoot camera problems</h2><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-mchlad460728\"><p>See the Apple Support article <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/HT211130\" class=\"URL\">If your built-in camera isn’t working on your Mac</a>.</p></div></div><p>To learn more about using the camera with specific apps, see the <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?product=facetime&amp;locale=en_US&amp;type=ddm\" class=\"URL\">FaceTime User Guide</a>, <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?product=messages&amp;locale=en_US&amp;type=ddm\" class=\"URL\">Messages User Guide</a>, and <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?product=photo-booth&amp;locale=en_US&amp;type=ddm\" class=\"URL\">Photo Booth User Guide</a>.</p><div class=\"LinkUniversal\"><strong>See also</strong><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=change-peoples-profile-pictures&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL3A930A6A&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Change the picture for you or others in apps on Mac</a></div></body>","tags":[{"type":"audience","refKey":"PUBLIC_USERS","tagPath":"audience/PUBLIC_USERS","title":"Public"}]}]},"categoryInfo":{"categories":["IP-Meta/DesignVersion/DesignVersion2","platform/mac","DisplayVersion/macOS Ventura 13","MetaFollow/MetaFollowOFF","ContentMode/liveContent","SupportSearchIndex/SupportSearchIndexON","ArchivalStatus/Archived","ExternalIndex/ExternalIndexOFF"],"categoryDictionaries":[{"key":"SupportSearchIndexON","name":"SupportSearchIndexON","englishName":"SupportSearchIndexON","displayName":"SupportSearchIndexON","articleCount":"120736"},{"key":"liveContent","name":"Live Content","englishName":"Live Content","displayName":"Live Content","articleCount":"135880"},{"key":"IP-Meta","name":"IP-Meta","englishName":"IP-Meta","displayName":"IP-Meta","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"Con